# ===================================
# COMMENTS FOR TEAM
# ===================================
# This .gitignore is designed for a professional portfolio project
# It covers all major frameworks, tools, and sensitive files
#
# Key things to remember:
# 1. NEVER commit .env files or credentials
# 2. Keep build artifacts out of version control
# 3. Exclude OS-specific files that don't belong in the repo
# 4. Be careful with media files - optimize before committing
# 5. Regularly review and update this file as the project grows